*2006年12月至2007年1月期间，由于[[2006年恆春地震|2006年恆春地震]]影响，包括本光缆的多条海底光缆在台湾东南地区附近受损中断，亚洲的互联网服务和金融交易——尤其是外汇市场——受到严重影响。<ref name="ST20061230">{{cite web|title=網上銀行服務仍「斷纜」|url=http://www.singtao.com.hk/archive/fullstory.asp?andor=or&year1=2006&month1=12&day1=30&year2=2006&month2=12&day2=30&category=all&id=20061230a08|work=[[星島日報|星島日報]]|accessdate=2013-11-05|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6KtLTPAaf?url=http://www.singtao.com.hk/archive/fullstory.asp?andor=or|archivedate=2013-11-05|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://hk.news.yahoo.com/061227/12/1yxbr.html|title=韓股匯市受挫港交易無礙 星洲期貨受影響 「彭博」電訊一度中斷|work=[[明报|明报]]|date=2006-12-28|accessdate=2012-03-22|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070518152250/http://hk.news.yahoo.com/061227/12/1yxbr.html|archivedate=2007-05-18|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.integratednetworkcable.com/communications/the-unexpected-communications-snag|title=uakes disrupt Asia communications|publisher=Integrated Network Cable|accessdate=2015-06-25|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150626134753/http://www.integratednetworkcable.com/communications/the-unexpected-communications-snag|archivedate=2015-06-26|deadurl=yes}}</ref>

*2008年1月30日，本光缆及[[SEA-ME-WE_4|SEA-ME-WE 4]]在[[地中海|地中海]]段受到损害，导致来自中东和印度的互联网服务受到影响。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.cnn.com/2008/WORLD/meast/01/31/dubai.outage/index.html |title=Internet failure hits two continents |work=CNN |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080203141349/http://edition.cnn.com/2008/WORLD/meast/01/31/dubai.outage/index.html |archivedate=2008-02-03 |accessdate=2008-02-01 |deadurl=no }}</ref>据[[英國廣播公司新聞網|BBC新闻网]]报告，来自埃及70%和来自印度60%的流量受到影响。<ref name="BBC_News">{{cite news | title=Severed cables disrupt Internet | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/technology/7218008.stm | work=BBC News Online | publisher=BBC | date=2008-01-31 | accessdate=2008-01-31 | archive-date=2008-01-31 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080131231934/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/technology/7218008.stm | dead-url=no }}</ref>巴林、孟加拉国、科威特、巴基斯坦、卡塔尔、沙特阿拉伯及阿拉伯联合酋长国都有报告出现问题。<ref>{{cite news | title=Cable Break Causes Wide Internet Outage | url=http://www.nytimes.com/aponline/technology/AP-Internet-Outages.html | date=February 1, 2008 | author=The Associated Press via nytimes.com | accessdate=2008-02-01 | work=The New York Times}}</ref>互联网运营商无法立即确认中断原因，事后也没有公布原因，只能根据网络流量记录得知发生在UTC4:30至8:00之间。<ref name="Renesys">{{cite web|url=http://www.renesys.com/blog/2008/01/mediterranean_cable_break_1.shtml#more|title=Mediterranean Cable Break|accessdate=2008-01-31|last=Zmijewski|first=Earl|date=2008-01-30|work=Renesys Blog|publisher=Renesys|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080203133228/http://www.renesys.com/blog/2008/01/mediterranean_cable_break_1.shtml%23more#more|archivedate=2008-02-03|deadurl=yes}}</ref>根据报道，怀疑是在亚历山大港附近有船只抛锚导致光缆中断。<ref name="BBC_News" /><ref name="TOI">{{Cite news|title=Cable damage hits Internet connectivity|work=The Times of India|accessdate=2008-01-31|date=2008-01-31|url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2008-01-31/india/27757001_1_cable-damage-hits-internet-undersea-cables-internet-users|archive-date=2012-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023061533/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2008-01-31/india/27757001_1_cable-damage-hits-internet-undersea-cables-internet-users|dead-url=no}}</ref>根据[[法新社|法新社]]，科威特政府将该事件归咎于“天气条件和海上交通”原因。<ref name="AFP">{{Cite news|title=Indian outsourcing sector hit by Internet disruption|work=AFP|accessdate=2008-01-31|date=2008-01-31|url=http://afp.google.com/article/ALeqM5gadarOY4frbM-XSyXS0_wMfxpHig|archive-date=2008-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080203184552/http://afp.google.com/article/ALeqM5gadarOY4frbM-XSyXS0_wMfxpHig|dead-url=no}}</ref>而[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]报道，损伤点在亚历山大港至[[马赛|马赛]]之间。<ref name="NYT">{{Cite news|issn=0362-4331|last=Timmons|first=Heather|title=2 Communication Cables in the Mediterranean Are Cut|work=The New York Times|accessdate=2008-01-31|date=2008-01-31|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/01/31/business/worldbusiness/31cable.html?ref=business|archive-date=2017-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170103235955/http://www.nytimes.com/2008/01/31/business/worldbusiness/31cable.html?ref=business|dead-url=no}}</ref>埃及政府在所在水域发出禁止船只进入的限制。<ref name=Brauer>{{cite news|author=Brauer, David|title=High-tech mystery: Are terrorists behind recent Internet disruptions?|url=http://www.minnpost.com/stories/2008/02/04/771/high-tech_mystery_are_terrorists_behind_recent_internet_disruptions|work=MinnPost.com|publisher=MinnPost|date=February 4, 2008|accessdate=2008-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080207074247/http://www.minnpost.com/stories/2008/02/04/771/high-tech_mystery_are_terrorists_behind_recent_internet_disruptions|archive-date=2008-02-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

*2008年1月31日，又再报告FALCON段在迪拜55千米外的光缆中断，<ref>{{Cite news |title= Update on Submarine Cable Cut |work= Daily Bulletin |publisher= Flag Telecom |date= February 6, 2008 |url= http://www.flagtelecom.com/index.cfm?channel=4328&NewsID=27492 |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20080219061824/http://www.flagtelecom.com/index.cfm?channel=4328&NewsID=27492 |archivedate= 2008-02-19 |accessdate= October 5, 2013 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url= http://edition.cnn.com/2008/WORLD/meast/02/01/internet.outage/index.html |work= CNN |title= Third undersea Internet cable cut in Mideast |date= February 1, 2008 |accessdate= 2010-05-02 |archive-date= 2009-10-03 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20091003213509/http://edition.cnn.com/2008/WORLD/meast/02/01/internet.outage/index.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>已先派出两艘修理船前往修理。<ref>{{Cite news |title= Work begins to repair severed net |date= February 5, 2008 |work= BBC News |url= http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/technology/7228315.stm |accessdate= October 5, 2013 |archive-date= 2015-08-08 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150808030322/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/technology/7228315.stm |dead-url= no }}</ref>

*2008年11月19日，包括本光缆和[[SEA-ME-WE_4|SEA-ME-WE 4]], [[SEA-ME-WE_3|SEA-ME-WE 3]]的多条光缆在地中海的区段损坏导致中东及印度地区的互联网服务受到影响。<ref name="BBC20081219">{{cite news | title = Severed cable disrupts net access | work = [[BBC_News_Online|BBC News Online]] | publisher = BBC | date = 2008-12-19 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/technology/7792688.stm | accessdate = 2008-12-21 | archive-date = 2008-12-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081220171653/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/technology/7792688.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref>当时无法确认损坏原因，虽然[[马耳他|马耳他]]附近曾检测到地震现象，<ref name="BBC20081219"/>但怀疑是船只抛锚或者渔船拖网时将光缆损坏。<ref name="BBC20081223">{{cite news | title = Third subsea cable repairs begin | work = [[BBC_News_Online|BBC News Online]] | publisher = BBC | date = 2008-12-23 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/technology/7797162.stm | accessdate = 2008-12-27 | archive-date = 2008-12-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081226022731/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/technology/7797162.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref>根据Reliance Globalcom的消息，断点位于亚历山大港和巴勒莫之间，最终于格林威治时间2008年12月29日14:15完成修复，光缆通信恢复正常服务。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.iglobalcom.relianceglobalcom.com/iglobalcom/cableupdate.html |title=Reliance Globalcom Cable Update Page |accessdate=2008-12-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090103005834/http://www.iglobalcom.relianceglobalcom.com/iglobalcom/cableupdate.html |archivedate=2009-01-03 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

